{"title":"献给英雄的诗——读王杰同志日记有感","authors":["顾工"],"dates":[{"year":1965,"month":11,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给英雄的诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——读王杰同志日记有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顾工"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄日记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光烈焰中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃出多少英雄；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代风雨里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创立无数奇功。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻英雄日记，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看红心呯呯跃动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读战士壮语，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听春雷响声隆隆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命献身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死比泰山更重；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"握枪抬头看，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满眼翠柏青松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命朝阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑灯学毛选，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光照满屋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士不知倦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星移又日出……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身影更高大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干劲更充足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王杰跟党走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山河齐让路！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处学雷锋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并肩上征途；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命朝阳升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辉耀云水怒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光辉形象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士和民兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"情比手足亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警惕海盗和飞贼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"武艺要练精。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河边试地雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王杰来传经，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级兄弟齐围拢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个个心连心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绊线固定好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引信猛颠动；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷瞬间要爆炸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎救众弟兄？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起董存瑞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"舍身举炸药；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起黄继光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"堵枪挺前胸……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王杰张双臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扑向火光中；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄形象冲天起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巍巍盖山峰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗志高昂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地雷连天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀声震峻岭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民兵斗志更高昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阔步大练兵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记住英雄姓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫忘烈士名，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗红心变万颗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人闹革命。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗卷风云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刀枪闪光明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼世界唱军歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利向前进……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}